text: Most useless insurance company. Not recommended to take the insurance. Trying to call/email them to make a specialist appointment for last 5 days. Not a single time got the call connected. What is a point if you can't respond to customers need.
Their representatives will ask you for Referrals before even doing a good job. Very Intrusive and uncomfortable doing business with them.

New Office. Nice infrastructure and Environment. Have free shuttle service for employees to commute from home. Also have lunch time free shuttle service to employees to commute between office & Payalebar MRT
It is an office for the staff ONLY. Does not serves walk-in or enquiry. No customers service counter. Please update the address to refer customers to the right place.

Location of customer service moved but I was not informed. Counter staff informed new location at Paya Lebar Square but actually its quite a walk from Paya Lebar Square. It was not even beside it. It s related to the building opposite to Tg Katong Shopping Centre.
